    ```bash
    curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"itemId": "item1", "quantity": 0}'
    ```

- **Item Out of Stock**:
    ```bash
    curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/orders -H "Content-Type: application/json" -d '{"itemId": "item2", "quantity": 1}'
    ```

